      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected based on rotating machinery benchmark literature. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model used; sensitivity to model constants assessed via ±10% parameter perturbation study. Model form uncertainty estimated at 12% of RH prediction. Required level 2 met."
    },
